{"tid":1788903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《中英聯合聲明》35 週年　英外相促中方尊重條文、與示威者對話","createTime":"2019-12-19T05:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T07:05:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"83a3b49e206ad69f6698b1686fe803751d853b13","tid":1788903,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"今日（12 月 19 日）是《中英聯合聲明》簽署 35 週年，英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）發表聲明，促請中國政府跟香港示威者對話，以及尊重《中英聯合聲明》條文。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在聲明當中提到，「香港正在經歷主權移交以來最長時期的動盪」，而「中英雙方簽署的協議已經清楚說明，香港的高度自治，權利以及自由會維持 50 年不變」。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，藍韜文又說「中國許下的承諾，包括言論自由、司法獨立以及法治制度，對於香港的繁榮以及生活方式都是必要的」。藍韜文表示，作為聯合聲明的其中一方，英國一直認真看待條文當中的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文並且說，「能保證香港未來成功和穩定的唯一方法，就是尊重條文，而且通過有意義的政治對話，去解決香港人的正當訴求」。<br />\n<br />\n在 8 月，藍韜文曾經致電特首林鄭月娥，對香港情況和示威行動表示關注，並促請展開獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n來源：路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-35-%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87-%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-35-%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%2587-%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6j2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=1b8e0709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-35-%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%2587-%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&h=db821ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-35-%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87-%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"d7fd063f5a82b12a0efc98fd1989ada521b7505e","tid":1788903,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n香港回歸英國啦<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17f575b04fb71c40b6d6a4fd36e324d0c7788ed","tid":1788903,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:28:20.000Z","msg":"原來［黃金經濟圈］唔包呢啲舖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1788841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1788841</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a86213c8e88a5ac24ca9bf8541cace376d91f51","tid":1788903,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"我哋冇人可以代表晒所有人，亦未有方法可以搵到代表。<br />\n泛民班老屎忽、誠哥、眾志、熱普誠加埋vs中共，除咗五大訴求之外冇乜斡旋空間。"},{"pid":"0d9c9ce07e6b80dc468e85887c5f96fe3b1d205a","tid":1788903,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7eaca3f38ee468c3a